<plot>In New Delhi, Gareth, a Welsh backpacker, is desperate to explore the exciting new world of India. Struggling with the heat and an upset stomach, he's conscious he still has a long way to go in terms of ticking off all the travel guide recommendations. Feeling pressure to experience the authentic India and live up to his somewhat wax-lyrical emails home, Gareth recognizes that he only has one hope: he has to get invited into a local's home. Gareth's desire to experience the 'Indian way of life' makes him anything but the open minded traveler he so desperately wants to portray.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?264282</url></doc>
